    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people or corporate bodies who own or run manufacturing plants for making devices used in a domestic context that facilitate such tasks as food preparation, food storage, cleaning, and grooming.</Note_Text>
